# RBAC

This module contains scripts for assigning and verifying Azure role-based access control (RBAC) permissions using PowerShell.

## Included Scripts

- `assign-role.ps1` – Assigns built-in or custom roles to users, groups, or service principals.
- `verify-role.ps1` – Validates role assignments and lists role definitions by scope.

## Purpose

These scripts demonstrate control over Azure resource permissions using modular automation, supporting least-privilege access patterns and administrative clarity.

## Notes

- Role assignments rely on valid principal IDs and scoped resource contexts.
- Verification supports troubleshooting and documentation of current access states.

